survey_response.review_text: We are very much satisfied with dental procedures of Dr Trupti. She is very professional and expert in various dental procedures. She charges reasonable amount for all procedures; good value for the money. My family members had the following dental procedures successfully at Magic Dental of Dr Trupti : Root canal treatment, Ceramic crown and bridge, partial dentures for upper jaw, fixing loose dental crown and Scaling & polishing. Recommend  Dr Trupti for all Dental procedures, especially nearby residents of MH Vihanga, MH Krishe and TNGO colony.

Dear Madam Dr. Trupti,
I can’t say enough about you, *** *** ** ******** compassionate *** *** *** ** *** ********* ************ ******* ** ********* *** ************** Wow   Dr. Trupti
you are amazing.
It takes a special person to be aware that you need to treat the comfort level of a patient before you can successfully diagnose a condition and prescribe a treatment plan. You are one of those very few special doctors. The kindness and caring you showed my person is not only appreciated but will never be forgotten.
* Dental Magic you are so good. Carepassion, you get it!
From, 
Ramesh P
C/o Ms Madhavi Krishna Pyla (Patient)

My gums were bleeding from 2-3 months. I  googled for home remedies but nothing works then i booked appointment and visited Dr Trupti. She explained that i was having gingivitis and she immediately cleaned my gums and polished them. It stopped bleeding the next day like some magic. If i had known all it required a proper cleaning, i wouldn't have hesitated at first, i wasted so much time trying internet solutions and worrying for no reason. This was my first time visit at dentist, and i am very much happy. Dr Trupti explained everything in a very friendly and professional manner. Also, She guided me and showed how to take care of my teeth so i won't get bleeding gums again. I will recommend her for sure. Don't think too much, if you're having a problem with your teeth. Must go to a dentist.

Fantastic doctor! I have had troubles with my wisdom tooth as it was half erupted and it would cause trouble every six months when the eruption forced will visit me. It was causing unfavourable conditions for my overall oral health. Doctor advised me right and helped me prepare mentally for something scary such as wisdom tooth extraction. She was very careful, patient and equally concerned of the discomfort that a patient goes through this journey. She took her time with my very firm tooth. The extraction was difficult but there was no swelling and pain was bearable. Overall I am very satisfied and I realise that I am in good hands. I'll consult her for my future needs as well.

I would like to recommend Dr.Trupti kashikar to my friends and relatives .I went to her for my wisdom tooth extraction 15 days before and found her to be very good in explaining the overall procedure .it went on smoothly without causing much discomfort and within 10days I am back to normal inspite of having all the four wisdom tooth extraction in one go . Thanks to her.

Texted her late at night saying I have pain. She accepted to see me next day at 9:30! This is what I love about my India. 
She was super efficient, knowledgeable and did not force me to go in for any expensive treatment. Just gave suggestions and went with my choice.
Will definitely be my choice of dentist for my family hereafter.

Dr. Trupti communicates with the patient during every step of a procedure, making sure they are okay and not in too much pain. She makes patients comfortable and relaxed without pain. I want to thank her efforts during my root canaI. I am so grateful for your help.

Dr Trupti is one of the most honest doctors. I trust her for her advice. She ensures she gives the treatment which is required and optimum - neither more or less. She was patient with me to determine the root cause of the issue and gave me the treatment while minimising the risk. Thank you very much and very pleased and relieved with the treatment.

Doctor Trupti is very good at her art. We visited her for my mom's root canal treatment. She spent a good amount of time understanding our case and making my mom feel comfortable.
The process was done in a single sitting. That's quite remarkable. The pricing was also reasonable and there is little or no wait time.
Overall - we would highly recommend Dr. Trupti
